==Finnish==
===Noun (obscene)===

#Wank, jerk-off, fuck-off etc. An annoying (usually male) person. See [[vittuilija]] and [[vittumainen]]. Milder than [[hintti]] but similarly used.
#A session of [[masturbation]]. "Kävin juuri runkulla." I just went and jerked off.
#A (usually male) person who masturbates a lot. 

Derived from the verb ''runkata'', "To wank".

===Related words===

''Runkkari'' wanker, literally a person who masturbates a lot, but usually means an annoying person.

